data.description: Uncover the Potential: Built-in 2014, this 3-bedroom 3 full bath Bi-Level Home in the Poconos, is a neutral canvas ready for your design ideas! With a spacious floor plan, large kitchen, a gas fireplace, and wood floors in the living room. Sliding door to the deck overlooking the yard and corner lot.The main floor bas a Master Bedroom with an ensuite bath, plus two additional bedrooms and full bath. The lower level with a bonus family room (needs flooring),full bath and laundry room needs your finishing touches. 2-car attached garage, Located in the picturesque and amenity-filled Pocono Farms Country Club with a lake, pool, clubhouse, gym, golf and more.
